      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.qYA6qBtNgc7kydMP]{Divine Champion}</p>\n<p>Choose a deity whose alignment is within one step of your own. If you have other abilities that require you to choose a deity (such as the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.themes.Item.aXgn2O25HtW7woS2]{priest} theme), you must choose the same deity.</p>\n<p>You are divinely protected, gaining a +1 enhancement bonus to saving throws with your lowest base saving throw bonus; if two or three of your base saving throw bonuses are tied for the lowest value, choose one of those categories to gain this bonus. This functions as and doesnâ€™t stack with the bonus provided by a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.equipment.Item.E9Y65ygZfMckhQ9g]{ring of resistance}, except the effect cannot be dispelled. At 6th level and every 4 levels thereafter, the bonus increases by 1.</p>"
